Class HtmlPrinter

  • java.lang.Object

    public class HtmlPrinter
extends XMLPrinter
implements ExtendedXMLBuilder
    Class for building HTML fragments. essentially a StringBuilder with additional methods to do html quoting so that the input can't corrupt the html structure or insert unwanted content like scripts.
